I"ú<p>Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Â Recently, Iâ€™m working on R Shiny to design a Web App. I found the example of selectInput shown on <a href="http://shiny.rstudio.com/reference/shiny/latest/selectInput.html" target="_blank">Shiny Reference</a> is not helpful once we have a list of items like <a href="/gytcrt.github.io/public/files/countries.txt" target="_blank">this</a>.</p>

